			<img src="/images/sand-03.jpg" alt="A wide sandy beach under a moody clouded sky, a few people walking at the water's edge." />
		</figure>
	</div>

	<p>
		Beyond Granadella, the coast holds dozens more — <strong>wild</strong>
		calas reached only on foot, <strong>busy</strong> resort beaches with
		their own particular charm, working harbours, long ribbons of
		dune-backed sand. The pictures below are from our own walks along this
		stretch. We've left the place names off on purpose. <strong>Ask us
		where they are</strong> — and we'll take you there.
	</p>

